metadata.dc:description: We report a 60-years-old patient with a not repaired exstrophic bladder, who develops an adenocarcinoma on his bladder and review of the literature.
metadata.dc:title: Adenocarcinoma vesical primario en extrofia vesical no corregida.
[Primary bladder adenocarcinoma in unreconstructed exstrophic bladder].
